		<title>Officials say foreigners own only 6% of Koh Pha Ngan following locals&#8217; concerns</title>
		<link>https://thethaiger.com/news/south/koh-pha-ngan-foreign-land-ownership-concerns-addressed</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Petch Petpailin]]></dc:creator>
