		<category><![CDATA[Ratchaburi]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://thethaiger.com/?p=1002618</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>A man in Ratchaburi has warned others to carefully check hair dye products after he suffered a severe allergic reaction from a hair dye he bought online that left his scalp irritated, his face swollen, and fluid leaking from the dyed area. The case was shared on Facebook by a user named Khun Weng Khao &#8230;</p>
<p>The story <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/national/online-hair-dye-ratchaburi-severe-allergic-reaction">Online hair dye leaves Ratchaburi man with severe allergic reaction</a> as seen on <a href="https://thethaiger.com/">Thaiger News</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<figure><img src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170838.343.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Online hair dye leaves Ratchaburi man with severe allergic reaction | Thaiger" style="margin-bottom: 15px;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170838.343.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170838.343-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170838.343-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170838.343-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170838.343-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" width="1280" height="720" /><figcaption>Online hair dye leaves Ratchaburi man with severe allergic reaction<span class="copyright">Legacy</span></figcaption></figure><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1280" height="720" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170838.343.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Online hair dye leaves Ratchaburi man with severe allergic reaction | Thaiger" style="float:right; margin:0 0 10px 10px;" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170838.343.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170838.343-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170838.343-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170838.343-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170838.343-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /><p data-start="35" data-end="279">A man in Ratchaburi has warned others to carefully check <strong>hair dye products</strong> after he suffered a severe <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/world/china/changsha-woman-falls-into-coma-following-allergic-reaction-to-salon-hair-dye" target="_blank" rel="noopener">allergic reaction from a hair dye</a> he bought online that left his scalp irritated, his face swollen, and <strong>fluid leaking</strong> from the dyed area.</p>
<p data-start="281" data-end="572">The case was shared on Facebook by a user named Khun Weng Khao Tom Pla Zing Ratchaburi, who posted that the hair dye <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/national/lone-mites-alert-blood-sucking-pests-cause-severe-itching-and-spread-through-close-contact" target="_blank" rel="noopener">caused severe itching</a>, burning and swelling after he applied it.</p>
<p data-start="574" data-end="744">The post included a video showing his head wrapped in bandages as fluid was still leaking from the affected area. He said he was not attacking anyone but wanted to warn others to test products on the skin before using them.</p>
<figure id="attachment_1002640" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1002640" style="width: 1280px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1002640" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T171236.824.jpg" alt="A Ratchaburi man warned consumers to check online hair dye products after suffering a severe allergic reaction from an unregistered product." width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T171236.824.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T171236.824-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T171236.824-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T171236.824-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T171236.824-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1002640" class="wp-caption-text">Photo via Matichon</figcaption></figure>
<p data-start="746" data-end="979">Reporters contacted the poster today, May 13, and identified him as 44 year old Phichit, who owns a well-known fish porridge shop in Ratchaburi Municipality.</p>
<p data-start="981" data-end="1208">Phichit was still wearing white gauze around his head because fluid continued to seep from his scalp. He said he bought the <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/world/fda-warns-hair-colouring-enthusiasts-in-thailand-to-avoid-south-korean-products-that-cause-cancer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hair dye product</a> online after seeing it advertised as being made from natural extracts and sold at a low price.</p>
<p data-start="1210" data-end="1377">He used the product on May 9, applying it only to the front hair roots and sideburn area rather than his whole head. He said he washed it off after about five minutes.</p>
<p data-start="1379" data-end="1571">The next morning, Phichit woke up with tightness in his face and noticed fluid near his forehead. After checking in a mirror, he found redness and fluid coming from the roots of the dyed hair.</p>
<figure id="attachment_1002637" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1002637" style="width: 1280px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1002637" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170922.363.jpg" alt="A Ratchaburi man warned consumers to check online hair dye products after suffering a severe allergic reaction from an unregistered product." width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170922.363.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170922.363-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170922.363-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170922.363-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170922.363-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1002637" class="wp-caption-text">Photo via Amarin TV</figcaption></figure>
<p data-start="1573" data-end="1808">Believing he was allergic to the hair dye, he bought medicine and washed his hair with baby shampoo, but the symptoms did not improve. His face then began to swell, prompting him to see a doctor and ask for a doctor’s note.</p>
<div class="qMYqUG_convSearchResultHighlightRoot">
