<p data-start="2045" data-end="2270">He later contacted public health officials, who checked the product and found the hair dye had not been properly registered and did not recieve approval from the Food and Drug Administration (FDA).</p>
<p data-start="2272" data-end="2489">Phichit then filed a police report at Mueang Ratchaburi Police Station and contacted the page that sold the product.</p>
<figure id="attachment_1002636" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1002636" style="width: 1280px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1002636" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170942.579.jpg" alt="A Ratchaburi man warned consumers to check online hair dye products after suffering a severe allergic reaction from an unregistered product." width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170942.579.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170942.579-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170942.579-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170942.579-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/สำเนาของ-23-34-2026-05-13T170942.579-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1002636" class="wp-caption-text">Photo via <a href="https://www.amarintv.com/news/social/545784#google_vignette" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Amarin TV</a></figcaption></figure>
<p data-start="2272" data-end="2489">Amarin TV reported that the seller initially described it as a normal allergic reaction and advised him to buy medicine, but stopped responding after he sent photos showing the severity of his condition.</p>
<div class="qMYqUG_convSearchResultHighlightRoot">
<div class="" data-turn-id-container="request-WEB:369e55cd-24ee-4391-9961-9af25b1449a3-113" data-is-intersecting="true">
